    or their respective <b>Hector video</b>.<br><br>The <b>JP</b> strat is identical
    to the common <b>Game8/Nukemaru</b> strat.<br><br><b>Zenith Uptime</b>, <b>Brain
    Deluxe</b> and <b>Emergency Meeting</b> are optional strats<br>that use others
    as base but follow their respective raidplans by default.<br><br>If you want
