  m_text: This will let you choose how you want to resolve the Stacks and Defamations<br>that
    are tethered to players by the clones after the first arena split.<br><br><b>Hector/Brain
    Deluxe Uptime Idyllic</b> is identical to the strategy<br>from <b>Hector's video</b>
    and from the <b>Brain Deluxe</b> raidplan.<br><br><b>NA</b>, <b>EU</b> and <b>JP</b>
    strategies use their respective PF strats.<br>Either from Hector's videos, pastebins
    or raidplans.<br><br><b>Banana Codex</b> is basically a <i>flipped</i> <b>Hector
    Uptime Idyllic</b>,<br>it is also the same strat used by <b>Emergency Meeting</b>,<br>but
    it is not a common strat used in PF.
